### 9. SOFT DELETE PATTERN

All models implement soft deletes using `deleted_at` timestamp:

```typescript
// Find active records only
const result = await this.knexRead<BaseStylesHashDto>(this.tableName)
  .where({ style_id: styleId })
  .whereNull('deleted_at')  // Only non-deleted records
  .first();

// Soft delete (mark as deleted)
await this.knexWrite(this.tableName)
  .where({ style_id: styleId })
  .whereNull('deleted_at')
  .update({
    deleted_at: this.knexWrite.fn.now(),
    updated_at: this.knexWrite.fn.now(),
  });
```

